value.name: Gen V
value.overview: At America's only college for superheroes, gifted students put their moral boundaries to the test, competing for the university's top ranking, and a chance to join The Seven, Vought International's elite superhero team. When the school's dark secrets come to light, they must decide what kind of heroes they want to become.

value.name: Country Life of Gen-Z
value.overview: A real-life "hipster" variety show where Gen-Z celebrities from the city become country Z by living in the countryside.
